		"dae": {
			"macro": {
				"name": "Spike Growth",
				"img": "icons/magic/nature/root-vines-grow-brown.webp",
				"type": "script",
				"scope": "global",
				"command": "if (!game.user?.isGM) return;\nconst src = \"if (!game.user?.isGM) return;\\nconst { token, segments, teleport } = event.data;\\nif (teleport) return;\\nconst actor = token.actor;\\nif (!actor) return;\\nconst totalFt = (segments ?? []).reduce((acc, s) => acc + (s.distance ?? 0), 0);\\nconst numDice = Math.floor(totalFt / 5) * 2;\\nif (numDice <= 0) return;\\nconst roll = await new Roll(numDice + \\\"d4\\\").evaluate();\\nconst feetLabel = Math.floor(totalFt / 5) * 5;\\nconst flavor = \\\"Spike Growth \\u2014 \\\" + numDice + \\\"d4 piercing (\\\" + feetLabel + \\\" ft through spikes)\\\";\\nif (typeof MidiQOL !== \\\"undefined\\\" && MidiQOL.DamageOnlyWorkflow) {\\n  new MidiQOL.DamageOnlyWorkflow(actor, token.object, roll.total, \\\"piercing\\\", [token.object], roll, { flavor });\\n} else {\\n  await roll.toMessage({ flavor, speaker: ChatMessage.getSpeaker({ token }) });\\n  await actor.applyDamage([{ type: \\\"piercing\\\", value: roll.total }]);\\n}\";\nfor (const ref of workflow.templateUuids ?? []) {\n  const region = typeof ref === \"string\" ? await fromUuid(ref).catch(() => null) : ref;\n  if (!region) continue;\n  if (region.behaviors.find(b => b.name === \"Spike Growth — Movement Damage\")) continue;\n  await region.createEmbeddedDocuments(\"RegionBehavior\", [{\n    name: \"Spike Growth — Movement Damage\",\n    type: \"executeScript\",\n    system: { events: [\"tokenMove\"], source: src },\n    disabled: false,\n  }]);\n}",
				"author": "vHqSHJMdmEO6Mk2C",
				"_id": null,
				"folder": null
			}
		}
	},
	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You drop seven sharp thorns or sticks to the ground, asking the land to obey your will. You gesture over the area and spikes sprout forth, blending in with their surroundings.</em></p><p><strong>Area Hazard</strong></p><ul><li><p>The spikes are camouflaged to look natural. Any creature that can't see the area at the time the spell is cast rolls a [[/check Perception]]{Perception} check against your spell save DC right before they would step into the spikes to notice the danger. Creatures who witness the spell can see the danger.</p></li><li><p>When a creature moves into a space occupied by the spikes, they take [[/damage 2d4 piercing]] damage for every 5 feet they travel.</p></li><li><p>The spikes create &amp;reference[difficultterrain].</p></li></ul><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> The radius of the spell increases by 5 ft. for each spell level above 2nd level.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
